reviewText:
It says in the description: This item contains the Renegade, first shape changing ball bearing yo-yo and our newly released "Kickin Tricks" video.
but only a vhs tape arrived. DO NOT BUY.
Only included a VHS ...a VHS! The White Renegade yo-yo was the reason I bought the item, and when I got the package, THERE WAS NO YO-YO! Do NOT buy. You're wasting your money!
